        <script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"http:\/\/schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Choose and Download Free Website Templates","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Browse our collection, choose the appropriate design from free responsive website templates. After getting to the product page, click on the checkout, and get it for free. The design is yours. "}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Install Free Web Template on Your Hosting","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"MotoCMS gives full freedom of choice to the clients. That&apos;s why you can take your hosting provider and domain name or choose from the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.motocms.com\/hosting\/\">recommended hosting providers<\/a> if you don&apos;t have one. More than that, along with free website templates, you can get MotoCMS free 1-year hosting if you write a secret word \"host me free\" in our chat. That&apos;s a bonus for the most persistent clients who carefully read the guides :) The biggest challenge is the template&apos;s installation. You can find more information about the installation and activation process in <a href=\"https:\/\/support.motocms.com\/hc\/en-us\/articles\/203594590--MotoCMS-3-Installation-Activation?_ga=2.36833187.2069708092.1597046661-1574419362.1595229186\">this helpful article<\/a> or use a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.motocms.com\/customer-services\/website-theme-installation\/\">professional theme installation service.<\/a>"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Customize Free Webpage Templates with Your Texts and Images","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"After installing the admin panel of free cms website templates, you can immediately edit your website pages. Add custom texts about you and your company. Inset custom images and photos or browse stick images from your media library. Feature your contact details and social media to engage your visitors. More than that, what is essential for NGO, crowdfunding, and charity organizations, you can add a PayPal Donation button to any of your website pages. If you need help with website customization, you can take advantage of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.motocms.com\/customer-services\/website-creation-template-customization\/\">MotoCMS template customization service<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.motocms.com\/customer-services\/web-copywriting-content-creation\/\">web copywriting<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.motocms.com\/customer-services\/custom-logo-design-branding\/\">custom logo design<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.motocms.com\/customer-services\/website-image-design-depositphotos\/\">website images<\/a>, or <a href=\"https:\/\/www.motocms.com\/customer-services\/website-onpage-seo-optimization\/\">on-page SEO optimization.<\/a>"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Publish Free CMS Template and Promote Your Website Online","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Your eye-candy website is fully ready to meet the visitors? Publish it online in a click and share it across your social media. Though, if you would like to get it done by a professional, check our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.motocms.com\/customer-services\/google-ads\/\">Google Ads service<\/a>, <a href=\"Facebook promotion campaign creation and management\">Facebook promotion campaign creation and management<\/a>, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.motocms.com\/customer-services\/social-media-brand-building\/\">and social media services.<\/a>"}}]}</script>

